      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The pain you feel is real, but the idea that your entire identity is worthless is a trap your mind is using to keep you from getting better. You are not defined by a single mistake; you are a person who has endured twenty years of effort, and that history still matters even if the final piece didn't fit. Please reach out to someone who can listen without judgment, because you deserve to be seen as more than just a failure.",
