    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not a mistake though. it was the core truth i thought i found. without that truth, i'm just a ghost walking around in a suit. everyone keeps telling me to 'find a new path' or 'start over' like i can just swap out my entire soul for something else. but there's nothing else. the silence is so loud now. it feels like the only honest thing left is the fact that i shouldn't even be here.",
